{ show-schema.ps1 #ps-winsqlite-show-schema

 `show-schema.ps1` uses my → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/winsqlite3_dll/PowerShell[PowerShell wrapper] for → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/winsqlite3_dll[`winsqlite3.dll`]
  to show the schema of an → development/databases/SQLite[SQLite database] using some data that is found in the meta table → development/databases/SQLite/internals/schema-objects/sqlite_master[`sqlite_master`].

  The script needs to be invoked in → Windows/PowerShell like so:
code {
.\show-schema.ps1 "$pwd/the.db"
code }
  
